quran[14{c,v,t}:
67,13,"tum khuwa chupkay se baat karo ya onche aawaz se ( Allah ke liye yaksaa hai ), woh to dilon ka haal taq jaanta hai"
67,14,kya wohi nah jaane ga jis ne peda kya hai? halaank woh bareek been aur bakhabar hai
67,15,"wohi to hai jis ne tumahray liye zameen ko tabay kar rakha hai, chalo uss ki chhaati par aur khao khuda ka rizaq, usi ke huzoor tumhe dobarah zindah ho kar jana hai"
67,16,kya tum iss se be khauf ho ke woh jo aasman mein hai tumhe zameen mein dhansa day aur yakayak yeh zameen jhakoley khanay lagey ?
67,17,kya tum iss se be khauf ho ke woh jo aasman mein hai tum par pathrao karne wali howa bhaij day? phir tumhe maloom ho jaye ga ke meri tanbeeh kaisi hoti hai
67,18,inn se pehlay guzray hue log jhutla chuke hain phir dekh lau ke meri girift kaisi sakht thi
67,19,kya yeh lau g apne oopar urrnay walay parindon ko par phelaaye aur sukrtay nahi dekhte? Rehman ke siwa koi nahi jo inhen thaamay hue ho wohi har cheez ka nigehbaan hai
67,20,"batao, aakhir woh konsa lashkar tumahray paas hai jo Rehman ke muqablay mein tumhari madad kar sakta hai? haqeeqat yeh hai ke munkareen dhokay mein parre hue hain"
67,21,"ya phir batao, kon hai jo tumhe rizaq day sakta hai agar Rehman apna rizaq rok le? darasal yeh log sir kashi aur haq se guraiz par uray hue hain"
67,22,"bhala socho, jo shakhs munh owndha-ay chal raha ho woh ziyada sahih raah panay wala hai ya woh jo sir uthaye seedha aik hamwar sarrak par chal raha ho ?"
67,23,"inn se kaho Allah hi hai jis ne tumhe peda kya, tum ko suneney aur dekhnay ki taqtin den aur sochnay samajhney walay dil diye, magar tum kam hi shukar ada karte ho"
67,24,"inn se kaho, Allah hi hai jis ne tumhe zameen mein phelaya aur isi ki taraf tum samete jao ge"
67,25,"yeh kehte hain"" agar tum sachey ho to batao yeh wada kab poora hoga? """
67,26,"kaho,"" iss ka ilm to Allah ke paas hai, mein to bas saaf saaf khabardaar kar dainay wala hon """
